_13514/2505.13514_induction_head_toxicity_repetition_curse_manifest.txt\nSplitting PDF: papers/2404.10859_forcing_diffuse_distributions.pdf\nTotal pages: 20\nPages per chunk: 3\nCreated 7 chunk files in: papers/pages/2404_10859\nManifest: papers/pages/2404_10859/2404.10859_forcing_diffuse_distributions_manifest.txt\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
